Big Brother Naija 2020 housemate, Lucy has revealed that Ka3na is the only evicted housemate she would love to bring back to the house if given the opportunity. Speaking during her diary session on Monday, Lucy who became too emotional when asked which of the evicted housemates she wants back into the house said Ka3na was the only true friend she had in the house. According to her, Ka3na was the only one she felt true friendship with. “Ka3na is the only housemate I am ready to do anything to make sure she gets back into the house. “If I have the power I will trade everyone else for her. “She was the only one that made me feel loved and she always looked out for me,” she said.
